          "type": "thinking",
          "thinking": "I need to search more broadly. Let me think about what kind of split reimbursement scenario I should look for.\n\nThe key rule is Article 11 of the expense reimbursement policy:\n- Same employee, same expense type, within 7 days, 2+ records\n- Combined amount reaches the \"较高审批线\" (higher approval line) from the authorization management appendix\n\nThe approval levels in 附件二:\n- AR-01: 0~3000, 部门经理\n- AR-02: ≥3000~<10000, 部门经理+财务复核\n- AR-03: ≥10000~<50000, 部门总经理\n- AR-04: ≥50000~<200000, 分管副总\n- AR-05: ≥200000, 总经理办公会\n\nThe \"较高审批线\" would mean that if you split one expense into multiple parts, and the combined total should have required a higher level of approval than what the individual parts required.\n\nLet me look for patterns more efficiently. I'll search for employees who filed multiple similar expenses within 7 days.\n\nLet me look at specific employees who might have multiple expenses within a short period.",
